p: Data is expressed as mean and standard error of the means (SEM). Normality and homogeneity of variances were tested using the Shapiro–Wilk and Levene tests, respectively. Data were analyzed by one-way ANOVA followed by Tukey’s multiple range test at a 1% probability level. All statistical analyses were performed using SPSS 22.0 software package (IBM, Chicago, IL, USA).
